{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1682-10b_086"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Lettre du Berger Fleuriste, à la Nymphe des Bruyeres"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", octobre 1682 (seconde partie) [tome 12], p. 86-92."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Je vous envoye une Lettre qui porte sa recommandation par les Noms sous lesquels elle est écrite. Ils vous sont connus, & je n’ay rien plus à vous dire, pour vous préparer à une lecture agréable."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "LETTRE"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/lb[1]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[2]", "text": "DU BERGER"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/lb[2]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[3]", "text": "FLEURISTE,"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/lb[3]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "A la Nymphe des Bruyeres"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sc"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[4]", "text": ","}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/lb[4]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[5]", "text": "En luy envoyant une Discretion"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/lb[5]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[6]", "text": "qu’il luy devoit."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Apres avoir bien pensé, belle Nymphe, à ce que je devois vous donner pour demeurer quitte de la discretion que vous m’avez gagnée"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": ","}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": " J’ay rebuté tous les Rubans,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "  L’Eventail & les Gans,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "La Poudre, la Pommade, & la galante Mouche,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Les Parfums, les Bouquets, le Bal, & le Cadeau ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Car enfin qu’a pour vous tout cela de nouveau ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": " Cependant la nouveauté touche,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": " Et fait trouver un Présent beau."}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/ab[1]", "tag": "ab", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/ab[1]/text()[1]", "text": "***"}], "attributes": {"type": "ornament"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": " J’ay donc jugé que pour vous plaire,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Il ne vous faloit rien qui vous fust ordinaire ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": " Et resvant tout le long du jour"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "  A cette grande affaire,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "J’ay conclu qu’il falloit vous donner de l’amour."}]}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Hé bien, Madame, ce Présent n’est-il pas honneste ? Ne le recevrez-vous pas avec joye, & seriez-vous Personne à faire de la façon pour prendre ce qui vous est si bien deû"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/text()[1]", "text": " ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": " L’amour que l’on donne est si doux,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": " Que rien d’égal ne se sent dans la vie."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous en pouvez juger, tout se rend à vos coups."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": " Aussi je m’en raporte à vous,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Qui faites ce Présent sans que l’on vous en prie."}]}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous répondrez peut-estre, qu’à la verité il y a bien de la douceur à donner de l’amour, mais qu’il n’y en a guére à en recevoir. Et pourquoy, belle Nymphe ? Un Présent change-t-il de nature en changeant de main ; & s’il est Or pour celuy qui l’ofre, est-il feüille de Chesne pour celuy qui le prend ? Si cela estoit de la sorte"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]/text()[1]", "text": ","}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": " Il n’est point de cœur délicat"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": " Qui n’en évitast le commerce."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": " Les Gens mesme d’humeur perverse"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": " Feroient gloire du Célibat."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": " Mais, grace aux Dieux, il est tel qu’on le donne ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Et quand il part d’une honneste Personne,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Il n’est pas comme un coup qu’on porte en un Combat,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": " Qui tient toûjours de la rudesse"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": " Qui nous offense & qui nous blesse."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[10]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[10]/text()[1]", "text": "Ne nous touchant alors que de traits innocens,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[11]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[11]/text()[1]", "text": " Loin de causer ny douleur ny tristesse,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[12]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[12]/text()[1]", "text": "Il comble de plaisir nos esprits & nos sens."}]}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[4]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[4]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[4]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Celuy, Madame, que je veux vous donner, est de cette nature ; & quand vous l’aurez pris, vous ne le garderez pas, si vous y trouvez de la diférence. Il me semble qu’on ne peut pas mieux dire, & que vous seriez blâmable de refuser d’en faire l’épreuve."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": " Agréez donc que je mette en vostre ame"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Quelques-uns de ses traits, quelque peu de sa flâme,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Et vous persuadez que je n’y mettray rien"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": " Que la mienne ne sente bien."}]}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[5]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[5]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[5]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "En attendant que j’apprenne vos intentions là-dessus, ayez la bonté de recevoir les Pommes d’Appie que je vous envoye. Elles sont du fonds de Flore, & presque aussi bonnes qu’elles sont belles. Mais, de grace, Madame, ne vous avisez pas d’accepter les Fruits pour la Discretion, & de rejetter l’amour comme un don surabondant."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": " L’amour vaut mieux que tous les fruits,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": " A moins qu’il ne les ait produits ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": " Et si vostre humeur ne s’accorde"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "A prendre également & les fruits & l’amour,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Ces Pommes deviendront des Pommes de discorde,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "J’en seray si jaloux, que j’en perdray le jour."}]}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[6]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[6]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[6]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Ce ne seroit pourtant pas une consolation pour moy, si vous me les renvoyiez. Un double refus me causeroit une double peine. J’aime mieux que ces heureux Fruits vous demeurent & vous servent, parce qu’ils me serviront peut-estre aussy."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Leur rouge vous fera penser à mon ardeur,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "  Leur jaune à ma langueur,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": " Et leur éclat à la brillante joye"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": " A qui je serois tout en proye,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": " Si j’avois comme eux le bonheur"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": " D’approcher vostre belle bouche."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": " Que peu ce grand bonheur les touche !"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": " Il me toucheroit jusqu’au cœur."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": " Jugez de nostre diférence,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[10]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[10]/text()[1]", "text": " Soyez sensible à ce qu’il est pour vous ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[11]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[11]/text()[1]", "text": " Un signe de reconnoissance"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[12]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[12]/text()[1]", "text": " M’empeschera d’estre jaloux."}]}]}]}]}]}